Object.Name: Sensors
Object.Description1: Control and read temperature sensor measurements. If "Stored Measurement Count" reaches maximum capacity (TBD), each new measurement causes oldest to be removed from list. Changes to "Enable" and "Measurement Interval" resources causes stored measurements to be cleared.
